citations:
    citation-grrm-ssm-brandon-sons:
        source: source-grrm-statements
        properties:
            locator: "So Spake Martin — SSM entry on Brandon Stark's children"
            text_from_source: "It'd be an exaggeration to say that Brandon died before he could have children. It's established in the books that he was no virgin. He could very well have left behind some little Snows in the various places he visited. But what's absolutely clear is that he had no legitimate children."
            accessed: "2026-03-10"
        notes: "GRRM's statement definitively rules out Brandon Stark as Jon Snow's father, since Jon was born near the end of Robert's Rebellion — months after Brandon's death. Brandon died before the war even began, and the war lasted close to a year. Any child Brandon fathered would have been born months before Jon."
